s at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP \r\n\r\nParibas, working in a number of areas including Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading desk and \r\n\r\nHedge Fund Prime Brokerage. Simon made his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010 and a second larger \r\n\r\npurchase in 2012. He joined Stewart and Chris on the NTB Capital team as a director in 2014, adding \r\n\r\nspecialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence.'),(2259,88,'_content_10_grid_item_3_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2260,88,'content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','70'),(2261,88,'_content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2262,88,'content_10_grid_item_4_name','Dane Crookham'),(2263,88,'_content_10_grid_item_4_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2264,88,'content_10_grid_item_4_title','Project Manager'),(2265,88,'_content_10_grid_item_4_title','field_5615541711750'),(2266,88,'content_10_grid_item_4_bio','Not Finished'),(2267,88,'_content_10_grid_item_4_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2268,88,'content_10_grid_item_4_avatar','70'),(2269,88,'_content_10_grid_item_4_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2270,88,'content_10_grid_item_5_name','Jasma Wadi'),(2271,88,'_content_10_grid_item_5_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2272,88,'content_10_grid_item_5_title','Serangan Headland Operations Manager'),(2273,88,'_content_10_grid_item_5_title','field_5615541711750'),(2274,88,'content_10_grid_item_5_bio','Jas has the biggest smile in Lombok and it is continuously affixed on his face, generating happy vibes \r\n\r\neverywhere he goes. Jas lives in Praya and is a vital link to the community surrounding our project at \r\n\r\nSerangan. His role is to facilitate harmonious relationships with the local community, hire and oversee local \r\n\r\nworkers and work with village chiefs (Kadus) and local government parties (Bupati), as well as major \r\n\r\ngovernment departments, such as; PU Department (roads), PLN (electricity), PDAM (water) and BPN (Land & \r\n\r\nTitles).'),(2275,88,'_content_10_grid_item_5_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2276,88,'content_10_grid_item_5_avatar','70'),(2277,88,'_content_10_grid_item_5_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2278,88,'content_10_grid_item_6_name','Kartini Lumban Raja'),(2279,88,'_content_10_grid_item_6_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2280,88,'content_10_grid_item_6_title','Office Manager and Bookkeeper Coordinator'),(2281,88,'_content_10_grid_item_6_title','field_5615541711750'),(2282,88,'content_10_grid_item_6_bio','Kartini is a rambunctious go-getter who will take on any project with gusto. She is a trusted and very vital \r\n\r\nmember of our team helping us negotiate the challenging hurdles of conducting business in Indonesia. Born \r\n\r\nin Sumatra and married to a local man from Gerupuk, she studied accounting at Universitas Advent \r\n\r\nIndonesia, Bandung and was previously working as the Country Director for Help Indonesia Foundation in \r\n\r\nJakarta.'),(2283,88,'_content_10_grid_item_6_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2284,88,'content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','70'),(2285,88,'_content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2286,88,'content_10_grid_item_7_name','Tamara Cox'),(2287,88,'_content_10_grid_item_7_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2288,88,'content_10_grid_item_7_title','Community Relations, Branding and Social Media Manager'),(2289,88,'_content_10_grid_item_7_title','field_5615541711750'),(2290,88,'content_10_grid_item_7_bio','Tamara has a history of community health care as a practicing podiatrist, specializing in Diabetes education.\r\n\r\nBorn and raised in Sydney’s North Shore with a strong background in health and fitness, her interests lie in \r\n\r\nhelping others. In particular she hopes to educate local communities regarding healthy living and \r\n\r\nenvironmental issues. Smart, logical, creative and caring she spearheads our CSR and PR efforts, linking us \r\n\r\nwith local charities. Responsible for our image and branding, Tamara managed the creation and continues to \r\n\r\nmaintain and update our website.'),(2291,88,'_content_10_grid_item_7_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2292,88,'content_10_grid_item_7_avatar','70'),(2293,88,'_content_10_grid_item_7_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2294,88,'content_10_grid_item_8_name','Maman'),(2295,88,'_content_10_grid_item_8_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2296,88,'content_10_grid_item_8_title','Contracts Administrator'),(2297,88,'_content_10_grid_item_8_title','field_5615541711750'),(2298,88,'content_10_grid_item_8_bio','Not Finished.'),(2299,88,'_content_10_grid_item_8_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2300,88,'content_10_grid_item_8_avatar','70'),(2301,88,'_content_10_grid_item_8_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2302,88,'content_10_grid_item','9'),(2303,88,'_content_10_grid_item','field_561553c81174d'),(2304,88,'content_11_title','Open Positions'),(2305,88,'_content_11_title','field_560da8ce2a001'),(2306,88,'content_11_content','<a class=\"btn btn-primary center-block\" style=\"width: 300px\" href=\"#\">Send Us An Email</a>'),(2307,88,'_content_11_content','field_560da8d32a002'),(2308,88,'content_12_title','Sign Up For Our Newsletter'),(2309,88,'_content_12_title','field_5626176d0d19b'),(2310,88,'content_12_content','<form class=\"form-inline\" style=\"text-align: center\">   <div class=\"form-group\">       <input type=\"email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"exampleInputEmail2\" placeholder=\"Email\">   </div>   <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Subscribe</button> </form>'),(2311,88,'_content_12_content','field_5626176d0d19c'),(2312,88,'content','a:13:{i:0;s:6:\"slider\";i:1;s:7:\"section\";i:2;s:5:\"image\";i:3;s:5:\"quote\";i:4;s:7:\"section\";i:5;s:5:\"image\";i:6;s:4:\"grid\";i:7;s:5:\"image\";i:8;s:4:\"grid\";i:9;s:5:\"image\";i:10;s:9:\"team_grid\";i:11;s:7:\"section\";i:12;s:18:\"plain_text_section\";}'),(2313,88,'_content','field_560da8a52a000'),(2318,89,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2319,89,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(2320,89,'_menu_item_object_id','39'),(2321,89,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2322,89,'