560da8ce2a001'),(3474,144,'content_4_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We amplify the buying power of our investors and connect them to sound investment strategies that are strengthened by Lombok’s unrivalled economic potential and environmental splendor. Our services are augmented with local expertise and resources, providing unprecedented access to exciting investment and lifestyle opportunities that would normally be beyond reach. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">“Keep your eyes on the stars and your feet on the ground.” – Theodore Roosevelt </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our vision is to exceed the expectations of our investors through a commitment to excellence in all that we do. Our desire is to be forerunners in South Lombok and its surrounds, forging a path of socially responsible, mutually beneficial and sustainable development that stands the test of time.</span></p>'),(3475,144,'_content_4_content','field_560da8d32a002'),(3476,144,'content_5_image','13'),(3477,144,'_content_5_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(3478,144,'content_6_title','Our Core Values'),(3479,144,'_content_6_title','field_560da9192a006'),(3480,144,'content_6_grid_item_0_grid_title','Priorities & Focus'),(3481,144,'_content_6_grid_item_0_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(3482,144,'content_6_grid_item_0_grid_content','Trust and integrity come first. You can’t have either without transparency. Success and finances will follow.'),(3483,144,'_content_6_grid_item_0_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(3484,144,'content_6_grid_item_1_grid_title','Making Money... The Right Way'),(3485,144,'_content_6_grid_item_1_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(3486,144,'content_6_grid_item_1_grid_content','You can make money without doing it wrong'),(3487,144,'_content_6_grid_item_1_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(3488,144,'content_6_grid_item_2_grid_title','Care & Respect'),(3489,144,'_content_6_grid_item_2_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(3490,144,'co