3777,146,'_content_0_slide_item_1_caption','field_561c12a2f851e'),(3778,146,'content_0_slide_item','2'),(3779,146,'_content_0_slide_item','field_561c1283f851c'),(3780,146,'content_1_title','This is Who We Are'),(3781,146,'_content_1_title','field_560da8ce2a001'),(3782,146,'content_1_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">NTB Capital is a private equity investment manager and developer providing unique lifestyle and investment opportunities in an emerging tourism hotspot presenting limitless growth potential. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our desire is to be forerunners in Lombok and its surrounding islands, forging a path of socially responsible and mutually beneficial development with minimal impact on the environment, creating a better future for the local inhabitants and a more rewarding experience for our clients.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our management team is a group of enterprising businessmen who don’t wear suits and are lucky enough to `work and live in a region of exceptional beauty. We strive to build a culture where success and lifestyle unite, turning dreams into reality.</span></p>'),(3783,146,'_content_1_content','field_560da8d32a002'),(3784,146,'content_2_image','20'),(3785,146,'_content_2_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(3786,146,'content_3_quote_text','Put your heart, mind and soul into even your smallest acts. This is the secret to success.'),(3787,146,'_content_3_quote_text','field_56154ef3023a8'),(3788,146,'content_4_title','Our Mission'),(3789,146,'_content_4_title','field_560da8ce2a001'),(3790,146,'content_4_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We amplify the buying power of our investors and connect them to sound investment strategies that are strengthened by Lombok’s unrivalled economic potential and environmental splendor. Our services are augmented with local expertise and resources, providing unprecedented access to exciting investment and lifestyle opportunities that would normally be beyond reach. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">“Keep your eyes on the stars and your feet on the ground.” – Theodore Roosevelt </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our vision is to exceed the expectations of our investors through a commitment to excellence in all that we do. Our desire is to be forerunners in South Lombok and its surrounds, forging a path of socially responsible, mutually beneficial and sustainable development that stands the test of time.</span></p>'),(3791,146,'_content_4_content','field_560da8d32a002'),(3792,146,'content_5_image','13'),(3793,146,'_content_5_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(3794,146,'content_6_title','Our Core Values'),(3795,146,'_content_6_title','field_560da9192a006'),(3796,146,'content_6_grid_item_0_grid_title','Priorities & Focus'),(3797,146,'_content_6_grid_item_0_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(3798,146,'content_6_grid_item_0_grid_content','Trust and integrity come first. You can’t have either without transparency. Success and finances will follow.'),(3799,146,'_content_6_grid_item_0_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(3800,146,'content_6_grid_item_1_grid_title','Making Money... The Right Way'),(3801,146,'_content_6_grid_item_1_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(3802,146,'content_6_grid_item_1_grid_content','You can make money without doing it wrong'),(3803,146,'_content_6_grid_item_1_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(3804,146,'content_6_grid_item_2_grid_title','Care & Respect'),(3805,146,'_content_6_grid_item_2_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(3806,146,'content_6_grid_item_2_grid_content','It is the people that make the company. People are valuable; whether it is our staff, our clients or the little old lady in the village.'),(3807,146,'_content_6_grid_item_2_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(3808,146,'content_6_grid_item_3_grid_title','Be Excellent'),(3809,146,'_content_6_grid_item_3_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(3810,146,'content_6_grid_item_3_grid_content','We don’t 