\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#\">Learn More</a>'),(6333,201,'_content_0_slide_item_0_caption','field_561c12a2f851e'),(6334,201,'content_0_slide_item','1'),(6335,201,'_content_0_slide_item','field_561c1283f851c'),(6336,201,'content_1_title','This is Who We Are'),(6337,201,'_content_1_title','field_560da8ce2a001'),(6338,201,'content_1_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">NTB Capital is a private equity investment manager and developer providing unique lifestyle and investment opportunities in an emerging tourism hotspot presenting limitless growth potential. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our desire is to be forerunners in Lombok and its surrounding islands, forging a path of socially responsible and mutually beneficial development with minimal impact on the environment, creating a better future for the local inhabitants and a more rewarding experience for our clients.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our management team is a group of enterprising businessmen who don’t wear suits and are lucky enough to `work and live in a region of exceptional beauty. We strive to build a culture where success and lifestyle unite, turning dreams into reality.</span></p>'),(6339,201,'_content_1_content','field_560da8d32a002'),(6340,201,'content_2_image','151'),(6341,201,'_content_2_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(6342,201,'content_3_quote_text','<p class=\"quote-text\">Put your heart, mind and soul into even your smallest acts. This is the secret to success.</p>'),(6343,201,'_content_3_quote_text','field_56154ef3023a8'),(6344,201,'content_4_title','Our Mission'),(6345,201,'_content_4_title','field_560da8ce2a001'),(6346,201,'content_4_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We amplify the buying power of our investors and connect them to sound investment strategies that are strengthened by Lombok’s unrivalled economic potential and environmental splendor. Our services are augmented with local expertise and resources, providing unprecedented access to exciting investment and lifestyle opportunities that would normally be beyond reach. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">“Keep your eyes on the stars and your feet on the ground.” – Theodore Roosevelt </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our vision is to exceed the expectations of our investors through a commitment to excellence in all that we do. Our desire is to be forerunners in South Lombok and its surrounds, forging a path of socially responsible, mutually beneficial and sustainable development that stands the test of time.</span></p>'),(6347,201,'_content_4_content','field_560da8d32a002'),(6348,201,'content_5_image','13'),(6349,201,'_content_5_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(6350,201,'content_6_title','Our Core Values'),(6351,201,'_content_6_title','field_560da9192a006'),(6352,201,'content_6_grid_item_0_grid_title','Care & Respect'),(6353,201,'_content_6_grid_item_0_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6354,201,'content_6_grid_item_0_grid_content','It is the people that make the company. People are valuable; whether it is our staff, our clients or the little old lady in the village.'),(6355,201,'_content_6_grid_item_0_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6356,201,'content_6_grid_item_1_grid_title','Be Resilient'),(6357,201,'_content_6_grid_item_1_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6358,201,'content_6_grid_item_1_grid_content','If you are disciplined, adaptable, diligent and willing to persevere in the face of opposition, nothing will stop you.'),(6359,201,'_content_6_grid_item_1_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6360,201,'content_6_grid_item_2_grid_title','Making Money... The Right Way'),(6361,201,'_content_6_grid_item_2_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6362,201,'content_6_grid_item_2_grid_content','You can make money without doing it wrong'),(6363,201,'_content_6_grid_item_2_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6364,201,'content_6_grid_item_3_grid_title','Priorities & Focus'),(6365,201,'_content_6_grid_item_3_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6366,201,'content_6_grid_item_3_grid_content','Trust and integrity come first. You can’t have either without transparency. Success and finances will follow.'),(6367,201,'_content_6_grid_item_3_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6368,201,'content_6_grid_item_4_grid_title','Be Excellent'),(6369,201,'_content_6_grid_item_4_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6370,201,'content_6_grid_item_4_grid_content','We don’t just want to be good. We want to be excellent.'),(6371,201,'_content_6_grid_item_4_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6372,201,'content_6_grid_item_5_grid_title','Every Journey Has Its Setbacks'),(6373,201,'_content_6_grid_item_5_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6374,201,'content_6_grid_item_5_grid_content','Be accountable, even if something was out of your control. Accept the situation and take responsibility. Be quick to start on the amazing thing you will do next.'),(6375,201,'_content_6_grid_item_5_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6376,201,'content_6_grid_item','6'),(6377,201,'_content_6_grid_item','field_560da9212a007'),(6378,201,'content_7_image','151'),(6379,201,'_content_7_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(6380,201,'content_8_title','This is What We Do'),(6381,201,'_content_8_title','field_560da9192a006'),(6382,201,'content_8_grid_item_0_grid_title','Investment'),(6383,201,'_content_8_grid_item_0_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6384,201,'content_8_grid_item_0_grid_content','We aggregate investors and increase their investment power offering a variety of asset backed investment strategies benefitting from the vast economic potential of South Lombok’s fast emerging property market.'),(6385,201,'_content_8_grid_item_0_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6386,201,'content_8_grid_item_1_grid_title','Land'),(6387,201,'_content_8_grid_item_1_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6388,201,'content_8_grid_item_1_grid_content','We subdivide large, prized parcels of land in beautiful, natural landscapes providing world-class property offerings that can be lived in now.'),(6389,201,'_content_8_grid_item_1_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6390,201,'content_8_grid_item_2_grid_title','Development'),(6391,201,'_content_8_grid_item_2_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(6392,201,'content_8_grid_item_2_grid_content','We use private equity to increase the value of our project land by building infrastructure and commercial developments such as hotels, shops and restaurants; whilst concurrently promoting private residential development.'),(6393,201,'_content_8_grid_item_2_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(6394,201,'content_8_grid_item','3'),(6395,201,'_content_8_grid_item','field_560da9212a007'),(6396,201,'content_9_image','152'),(6397,201,'_content_9_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(6398,201,'content_10_team_text','The People That Make It Happen'),(6399,201,'_content_10_team_text','field_561553c81174c'),(6400,201,'content_10_grid_item_0_name','Chris Berney'),(6401,201,'_content_10_grid_item_0_name','field_561553c81174e'),(6402,201,'content_10_grid_item_0_title','Founding Partner'),(6403,201,'_content_10_grid_item_0_title','field_5615541711750'),(6404,201,'content_10_grid_item_0_bio','Chris is a former equity trader at Dresdner Kleinwort (Commerzbank) in London and both trader/broker at Macquarie Bank in Hong Kong. After leaving Macquarie in 2009 he spent 3 years setting up the equity desks at Chinese brokerages before moving to Indonesia fulltime as partner at Elite Havens Lombok in 2013. Chris set up NTB Capital later in 2013 to pursue private equity-type returns.  Chris has known Stewart for 8 years, purchased his first Lombok property in January 2013 and brings to the team a wealth of knowledge in structuring deals, sales and capital raising.'),(6405,201,'_content_10_grid_item_0_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(6406,201,'content_10_grid_item_0_avatar','69'),(6407,201,'_content_10_grid_item_0_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(6408,201,'content_10_grid_item_1_name','David Mulligan'),(6409,201,'_content_10_grid_item_1_name','field_561553c81174e'),(6410,201,'content_10_grid_item_1_title','Director - General Manager'),(6411,201,'_content_10_grid_item_1_title','field_5615541711750'),(6412,201,'content_10_grid_item_1_bio','David is a former commercial real estate agent operating in Sydney for almost a decade. During this time, he\r\n\r\nwas a REINSW finalist in line for the Excellence in Commercial Sales and Leasing award and was a member of \r\n\r\nthe Property Council of Australia. David also worked as the National Sales & Customer Service Manager for a \r\n\r\nmajor Australian and US surfboard brand. David brings with him experience in both small and large business \r\n\r\nas well as practical skills and knowledge in a variety of key areas, notably; management, project \r\n\r\ndevelopment, marketing and sales.'),(6413,201,'_content_10_grid_item_1_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(6414,201,'content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','70'),(6415,201,'_content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(6416,201,'content_10_grid_item_2_name','Simon Barnes'),(6417,201,'_content_10_grid_item_2_name','field_561553c81174e'),(6418,201,'content_10_grid_item_2_title','Director'),(6419,201,'_content_10_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(6420,201,'content_10_grid_item_2_bio','Simon spent a total of 13 years in investment banking, including stints at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP \r\n\r\nParibas, working in a number of areas including Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading desk and \r\n\r\nHedge Fund Prime Brokerage. Simon made his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010 and a second larger \r\n\r\npurchase in 2012. He joined Stewart and Chris on the NTB Capital team as a director in 2014, adding \r\n\r\nspecialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence.'),(6421,201,'_content_10_grid_item_2_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(6422,201,'content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','70'),(6423,201,'_content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','field_56155435117