ia Manager'),(8807,233,'_content_10_grid_item_6_title','field_5615541711750'),(8808,233,'content_10_grid_item_6_bio','Tamara has a history of community health care as a practicing podiatrist, specializing in Diabetes education.\r\n\r\nBorn and raised in Sydney’s North Shore with a strong background in health and fitness, her interests lie in \r\n\r\nhelping others. In particular she hopes to educate local communities regarding healthy living and \r\n\r\nenvironmental issues. Smart, logical, creative and caring she spearheads our CSR and PR efforts, linking us \r\n\r\nwith local charities. Responsible for our image and branding, Tamara managed the creation and continues to \r\n\r\nmaintain and update our website.'),(8809,233,'_content_10_grid_item_6_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(8810,233,'content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','70'),(8811,233,'_content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(8812,233,'content_10_grid_item_7_name','Kartini Lumban Raja'),(8813,233,'_content_10_grid_item_7_name','field_561553c81174e'),(8814,233,'content_10_grid_item_7_title','Office Manager and Bookkeeper Coordinator'),(8815,233,'_content_10_grid_item_7_title','field_5615541711750'),(8816,233,'content_10_grid_item_7_bio','Kartini is a rambunctious go-getter who will take on any project with gusto. She is a trusted and very vital \r\n\r\nmember of our team helping us negotiate the challenging hurdles of conducting business in Indonesia. Born \r\n\r\nin Sumatra and married to a local man from Gerupuk, she studied accounting at Universitas Advent \r\n\r\nIndonesia, Bandung and was previously working as the Country Director for Help Indonesia Foundation in \r\n\r\nJakarta.'),(8817,233,'_content_10_grid_item_7_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(8818,233,'content_10_grid_item_7_avatar','70'),(8819,233,'_content_10_grid_item_7_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(8820,233,'content_10_grid_item_8_name','Credo Woruntu'),(8821,233,'_content_10_grid_item_8_name','field_561553c81174e'),(8822,233,'content_10_gri