content_9_image','152'),(8942,239,'_content_9_image','field_560da8f72a004'),(8943,239,'content_10_team_text','The People That Make It Happen'),(8944,239,'_content_10_team_text','field_561553c81174c'),(8945,239,'content_10_grid_item_0_name','Chris Berney'),(8946,239,'_content_10_grid_item_0_name','field_561553c81174e'),(8947,239,'content_10_grid_item_0_title','Founding Partner'),(8948,239,'_content_10_grid_item_0_title','field_5615541711750'),(8949,239,'content_10_grid_item_0_bio','Chris is a former equity trader at Dresdner Kleinwort (Commerzbank) in London and both trader/broker at Macquarie Bank in Hong Kong. After leaving Macquarie in 2009 he spent 3 years setting up the equity desks at Chinese brokerages before moving to Indonesia fulltime as partner at Elite Havens Lombok in 2013. Chris set up NTB Capital later in 2013 to pursue private equity-type returns.  Chris has known Stewart for 8 years, purchased his first Lombok property in January 2013 and brings to the team a wealth of knowledge in structuring deals, sales and capital raising.'),(8950,239,'_content_10_grid_item_0_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(8951,239,'content_10_grid_item_0_avatar','69'),(8952,239,'_content_10_grid_item_0_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(8953,239,'content_10_grid_item_1_name','David Mulligan'),(8954,239,'_content_10_grid_item_1_name','field_561553c81174e'),(8955,239,'content_10_grid_item_1_title','Director - General Manager'),(8956,239,'_content_10_grid_item_1_title','field_5615541711750'),(8957,239,'content_10_grid_item_1_bio','David is a former commercial real estate agent operating in Sydney for almost a decade. During this time, he\r\n\r\nwas a REINSW finalist in line for the Excellence in Commercial Sales and Leasing award and was a member of \r\n\r\nthe Property Council of Australia. David also worked as the National Sales & Customer Service Manager for a \r\n\r\nmajor Australian and US surfboard brand. David brings with him experience in both small and large business \r\n\r\nas well as practical skills and knowledge in a variety of key areas, notably; management, project \r\n\r\ndevelopment, marketing and sales.'),(8958,239,'_content_10_grid_item_1_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(8959,239,'content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','70'),(8960,239,'_content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(8961,239,'content_10_grid_item_2_name','Simon Barnes'),(8962,239,'_content_10_grid_item_2_name','field_561553c81174e'),(8963,239,'content_10_grid_item_2_title','Director'),(8964,239,'_content_10_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(8965,239,'content_10_grid_item_2_bio','Simon spent a total of 13 years in investment banking, including stints at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP \r\n\r\nParibas, working in a number of areas including Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading desk and \r\n\r\nHedge Fund Prime Brokerage. Simon made his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010 and a second larger \r\n\r\npurchase in 2012. He joined Stewart and Chris on the NTB Capital team as a director in 2014, adding \r\n\r\nspecialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence.'),(8966,239,'_content_10_grid_item_2_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(8967,239,'content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','70'),(8968,239,'_content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(8969,239,'content_10_grid_item_3_name','Dane Crookham'),(8970,239,'_content_10_grid_item_3_name','field_561553c81174e'),(8971,239,'content_10_grid_item_3_title','Project Manager'),(8972,239,'_content_10_grid_item_3_title','field_5615541711750'),(8973,239,'content_10_grid_item_3_bio','Not Finished'),(8974,239,'_content_10_grid_item_3_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(8975,239,'content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','70'),(8976,239,'_content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(8977,239,'content_10_grid_item_4_name','Maman'),(8978,239,'_content_10_grid_item_4_name','field_561553c81174e'),(8979,239,'content_10_grid_item_4_title','Contracts Administrator'),(8980,239,'_content_10_grid_item_4_title','field_5