ist in line for the Excellence in Commercial Sales and Leasing award and was a member of \r\n\r\nthe Property Council of Australia. David also worked as the National Sales & Customer Service Manager for a \r\n\r\nmajor Australian and US surfboard brand. David brings with him experience in both small and large business \r\n\r\nas well as practical skills and knowledge in a variety of key areas, notably; management, project \r\n\r\ndevelopment, marketing and sales.'),(9896,255,'_content_10_grid_item_1_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(9897,255,'content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','70'),(9898,255,'_content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(9899,255,'content_10_grid_item_2_name','Simon Barnes'),(9900,255,'_content_10_grid_item_2_name','field_561553c81174e'),(9901,255,'content_10_grid_item_2_title','Director'),(9902,255,'_content_10_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(9903,255,'content_10_grid_item_2_bio','Simon spent a total of 13 years in investment banking, including stints at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP \r\n\r\nParibas, working in a number of areas including Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading desk and \r\n\r\nHedge Fund Prime Brokerage. Simon made his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010 and a second larger \r\n\r\npurchase in 2012. He joined Stewart and Chris on the NTB Capital team as a director in 2014, adding \r\n\r\nspecialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence.'),(9904,255,'_content_10_grid_item_2_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(9905,255,'content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','70'),(9906,255,'_content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(9907,255,'content_10_grid_item_3_name','Dane Crookham'),(9908,255,'_content_10_grid_item_3_name','field_561553c81174e'),(9909,255,'content_10_grid_item_3_title','Project Manager'),(9910,255,'_content_10_grid_item_3_title','field_5615541711750'),(9911,255,'content_10_grid_item_3_bio','Not Finished'),(9912,255,'_content_10_grid_item_3_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(9913,255,'cont