nal Sales & Customer Service Manager for a prominent  Australian and  US surfboard  brand. David  brings  with  him experience in both small and large business as well as practical skills and knowledge in a variety of key areas, notably;  management,  project  development,  marketing  and  sales. His calm,  measured and practical approach is the perfect ying to the yang of his entrepreneurial business partner. '),(12759,326,'_content_5_grid_item_1_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(12760,326,'content_5_grid_item_1_avatar',''),(12761,326,'_content_5_grid_item_1_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(12762,326,'content_5_grid_item_2_name','Simon Barnes'),(12763,326,'_content_5_grid_item_2_name','field_561553c81174e'),(12764,326,'content_5_grid_item_2_title','Director'),(12765,326,'_content_5_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(12766,326,'content_5_grid_item_2_bio','Simon spent a total of 13 years in investment banking, including stints at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP Paribas, working  in a number of areas including  Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading  desk and Hedge  Fund Prime Brokerage.  Simon made   his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010  and a second  larger purchase  in  2012. He joined David  and Chris on  the NTB Capital  team as a  director in 2014,  adding specialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence. '),(12767,326,'_content_5_grid_item_2_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(12768,326,'content_5_grid_item_2_avatar',''),(12769,326,'_content_5_grid_item_2_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(12770,326,'content_5_grid_item_3_name','Dane Crookham'),(12771,326,'_content_5_grid_item_3_name','field_561553c81174e'),(12772,326,'content_5_grid_item_3_title','Social Media & Marketing'),(12773,326,'_content_5_grid_item_3_title','field_5615541711750'),(12774,326,'content_5_grid_item_3_bio','Dane is a former builder from Sydney with over 15 years of construction experience. Now living in Bali, he is our marketing whiz with the vision, imagination 