id_item_5_grid_title','field_560da9302a008'),(13250,333,'content_4_grid_item_5_grid_content','Be accountable, even if something was out of your control. Accept the situation and take responsibility. Be quick to start on the amazing thing you will do next.'),(13251,333,'_content_4_grid_item_5_grid_content','field_560da93b2a009'),(13252,333,'content_4_grid_item','6'),(13253,333,'_content_4_grid_item','field_560da9212a007'),(13254,333,'content_5_team_text','Meet Our Team'),(13255,333,'_content_5_team_text','field_561553c81174c'),(13256,333,'content_5_grid_item_0_name','Chris Berney'),(13257,333,'_content_5_grid_item_0_name','field_561553c81174e'),(13258,333,'content_5_grid_item_0_title','Founding Partner'),(13259,333,'_content_5_grid_item_0_title','field_5615541711750'),(13260,333,'content_5_grid_item_0_bio','Chris is a former equity trader at Dresdner Kleinwort (Commerzbank) in London and both trader/broker at Macquarie Bank in Hong Kong. After leaving Macquarie in 2009 he spent 3 years setting up the equity desks at Chinese brokerages before moving to Indonesia fulltime as partner at Elite Havens Lombok in 2013. Chris set up NTB Capital later in 2013 to pursue private equity-type returns.  Chris has known Stewart for 8 years, purchased his first Lombok property in January 2013 and brings to the team a wealth of knowledge in structuring deals, sales and capital raising.'),(13261,333,'_content_5_grid_item_0_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(13262,333,'content_5_grid_item_0_avatar',''),(13263,333,'_content_5_grid_item_0_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(13264,333,'content_5_grid_item_1_name','David Mulligan'),(13265,333,'_content_5_grid_item_1_name','field_561553c81174e'),(13266,333,'content_5_grid_item_1_title','Director - General Manager'),(13267,333,'_content_5_grid_item_1_title','field_5615541711750'),(13268,333,'content_5_grid_item_1_bio','David is a former commercial real estate agent who operated in Sydney for almost a decade. David  also  worked  as the National Sales & Customer Service Manager for a prominent  Australian and  US surfboard  brand. David  brings  with  him experience in both small and large business as well as practical skills and knowledge in a variety of key areas, notably;  management,  project  development,  marketing  and  sales. His calm,  measured and practical approach is the perfect ying to the yang of his entrepreneurial business partner. '),(13269,333,'_content_5_grid_item_1_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(13270,333,'content_5_grid_item_1_avatar',''),(13271,333,'_content_5_grid_item_1_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(13272,333,'content_5_grid_item_2_name','Simon Barnes'),(13273,333,'_content_5_grid_item_2_name','field_561553c81174e'),(13274,333,'content_5_grid_item_2_title','Director'),(13275,333,'_content_5_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(13276,333,'content_5_grid_item_2_bio','Simon spent a total of 13 years in investment banking, including stints at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP Paribas, working  in a number of areas including  Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading  desk and Hedge  Fund Prime Brokerage.  Simon made   his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010  and a second  larger purchase  in  2012. He joined David  and Chris on  the NTB Capital  team as a  director in 2014,  adding specialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence. '),(13277,333,'_content_5_grid_item_2_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(13278,333,'content_5_grid_item_2_avatar',''),(13279,333,'_content_5_grid_item_2_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(13280,333,'content_5_grid_item_3_name','Dane Crookham'),(13281,333,'_content_5_grid_item_3_name','field_561553c81174e'),(13282,333,'content_5_grid_item_3_title','Social Media & Marketing'),(13283,333,'_content_5_grid_item_3_title','field_5615541711750'),(13284,333,'content_5_grid_item_3_bio','Dane is a former builder from Sydney with over 15 years of construction experience. Now living in Bali, he is our marketing whiz with the vision, imagination  and skills to represent our core ideas to the outside world.'),(13285,333,'_content_5_grid_item_3_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(13286,333,'content_5_grid_item_3_avatar',''),(13287,333,'_content_5_grid_item_3_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(13288,333,'content_5_grid_item_4_name','Maman'),(13289,333,'_content_5_grid_item_4_name','field_561553c81174e'),(13290,333,'content_5_grid_item_4_title','Contracts Administrator'),(13291,333,'_content_5_grid_item_4_title','field_5615541711750'),(13292,333,'content_5_grid_item_4_bio','Maman (Fazlurrahman) was born in Lombok but spent 15 years in East Java. During that time he was educated at the State University of Malang where he completed a Bachelor in Building and Engineering, before working on several government infrastructure projects.  Maman adds vital local knowledge to our team, speaks three languages, and acts as a conduit for placable interaction between western and Indonesian cultural and language differences. Humble, hardworking and accommodating, he possesses the perfect personality for this challenging role.'),(13293,333,'_content_5_grid_item_4_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(13294,333,'content_5_grid_item_4_avatar',''),(13295,333,'_content_5_grid_item_4_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(13296,333,'content_5_grid_item_5_name','Franky Pandapotan Simamoran'),(13297,333,'_content_5_grid_item_5_name','field_561553c81174e'),(13298,333,'content_5_grid_item_5_title','Tax & Accounting'),(13299,333,'_content_5_grid_item_5_title','field_5615541711750'),(13300,333,'content_5_grid_item_5_bio','Franky is a vital member of the team. Enthusiastic and dependable, he helps out in a myriad of areas including some of the most important ones - finances and tax. Joining us from Jakarta and with experience in government departments, Franky\'s contribution has been invaluable.'),(13301,333,'_content_5_grid_item_5_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(13302,333,'content_5_grid_item_5_avatar',''),(13303,333,'_content_5_grid_item_5_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(133