=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<h3>Corporate Social Responsibility</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Corporate Social Responsibility is at the core of our values. It is an intentional decision to make a positive impact on the local environment and communities. In development projects, we will endeavor to train staff in hospitality, the English language, service of food and beverages, management and administration. Wherever possible we will implement environmentally friendly options regarding waste management, recycling, water and energy usage.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<h3>Community</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Whenever possible NTB Capital hires staff locally, particularly surrounding our projects. This provides economic benefit as well as creating a stable and friendly relationship with the nearby villages. Currently we hire local villagers in our investment projects as caretakers, security guards, land clearers, labourers and more. In addition, we are actively seeking opportunities to be responsible and improve the standard of life for local Indonesian communities.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<h3>Charities</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We support these amazing organisations and encourage our clients to join us.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Community','','inherit','closed','closed','','104-revision-v1','','','2015-11-10 19:01:33','2015-11-10 19:01:33','',104,'http://ntb.dev/104-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(179,1,'2015-11-10 19:05:30','2015-11-10 19:05:30','<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h3>Investment Case</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">South Lombok is fast approaching the start of a significant investment cycle, with strong growth potential expected over the next 10-15 years. Strong domestic demand and a growing Asian middle-class are compelling this imminent growth phase and providing fertile grounds for Lombok’s burgeoning tourism capabilities. 2014 marked the transition from early speculation to a legitimate property market as the first major developers broke ground in the south, coinciding with government infrastructure projects; and focus on the long awaited Mandalika project, which will bring a lot of international focus and attention on the regions beautiful beaches and its close proximity to the new international airport.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h3>Investment Strategies</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">With a substantial supply versus demand mismatch in hotel accommodation and commercial projects in South Lombok, particularly compared to the matured Bali tourist market; our key focus is hotel investments and land subdivisions, with secondary focus on distressed assets and land banking. Our attention is focused on due diligence and structuring our investments to minimize as much risk as possible, while generating accelerated increase for investors by driving infrastructure, development and foreign populace.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Investment Case & Strategies','','publish','closed','closed','','investment','','','2016-03-07 03:25:33','2016-03-07 03:25:33','',0,'http://ntb.dev/?page_id=179',0,'page','',0),(180,1,'2015-11-10 19:05:30','2015-11-10 19:05:30','','Investment Case & Strategies','','inherit','closed','closed','','179-revision-v1','','','2015-11-10 19:05:30','2015-11-10 19:05:30','',179,'http://ntb.dev/179-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(181,1,'2015-11-10 19:05:52','2015-11-10 19:05:52','<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<h3>Corporate Social Responsibility</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Corporate Social Responsibility is at the core of our valu